body: Another perfect day with my beautiful girlfriend! She's lucky to have someone who keeps her grounded
Excited for tonight's psychology study group! Learning so much this semester
Movie night with the girls was exactly what I needed!
Engineering project deadlines are approaching fast. Time to buckle down
Art gallery opening tonight! So excited to showcase my latest pieces

@joanieb Joan finally wore something decent today. Usually she dresses like she shops at thrift stores but I've been teaching her about style. Small improvements I guess. Her presentation was interesting too. Good thing I helped her practice or it would have been a disaster. She really needs to work on her confidence
Psychology research methods are challenging but fascinating
Fraternity community service event was a huge success today
